				<descriptionOfRestrictions xml:lang="en">The power station is located in the central region of Ningxia, China, where the average annual solar radiation is approximately 5955.80 MJ m2 a-1, and the annual average number of peak sunshine hours are 1718 h.</descriptionOfRestrictions>
				<descriptionOfRestrictions xml:lang="zh">该电站位于宁夏中部地区，年平均太阳辐射量约为5955.80 MJ m2 a-1，年平均日照高峰时数为1718h</descriptionOfRestrictions>
			</locationOfOperationSupplyOrProduction>
		</geography>
		<technology>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="en">The SoG-Si ingot casting process manufactures solar-grade multi-crystalline silicon ingots that are primarily used as raw materials for the production of multi-crystalline silicon photovoltaic (PV) cells. These PV cells are essential components in solar panels for converting solar energy into electricity. The data set is particularly relevant for the solar power industry, especially for companies involved in manufacturing and assessing the environmental impact of solar panels in grid-connected electricity generation systems.</technologicalApplicability>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="zh">太阳能级多晶硅铸锭的生产过程主要用于生产多晶硅光伏电池的原材料。这些光伏电池是太阳能电池板中转换太阳能为电能的重要组成部分。该数据集尤其适用于太阳能发电行业，特别是那些参与太阳能板制造和评估并网电力发电系统环境影响的公司。</technologicalApplicability>
			<referenceToTechnologyFlowDiagrammOrPicture type="source data set" refObjectId="4009d220-7de9-5168-60af-0a4f4738b7c4" uri="../sources/4009d220-7de9-5168-60af-0a4f4738b7c4.xml">
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="en">SUiJbzIljoVVdmxs9ric7xZUnTe.png</common:shortDescription>
			</referenceToTechnologyFlowDiagrammOrPicture>
		</technology>
