				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="zh">Yu, Z. et al. Life cycle assessment of grid-connected power generation from metallurgical route multi-crystalline silicon photovoltaic system in China. Applied Energy 185, 68–81 (2017).</common:shortDescription>
			</referenceToDataSource>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">Users should consider the regional solar radiation data and operating conditions specific to the central region of Ningxia, China when using this dataset. It is important to note that the data is designed for a multi-Si PV system with a specified lifespan of 30 years, serving as a study subject with a 10 MWp capacity. When integrating this data into LCA models, users must account for the functional lifespan and region-specific solar irradiance to accurately assess the environmental impacts of the PV system. Attention should be given to the methodological consistency with other datasets in the LCA and to the alignment with the goal and scope of the study concerning the use of metallurgical route multi-crystalline silicon.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">使用该数据集时，用户应考虑宁夏中部特定地区的太阳辐射数据和操作条件。需要注意的是，该数据旨在用于一个具有30年预定使用寿命的多晶硅光伏系统，该系统作为一个10 MWp容量的研究对象。在将这些数据集成到生命周期评估模型中时，用户必须考虑功能寿命和区域特定的太阳辐射，以准确评估光伏系统的环境影响。还应注意与生命周期评估中其他数据集的方法论一致性，以及确保与关于使用冶金路线多晶硅的研究目标和范围的一致性。</useAdviceForDataSet>
